SUMMARY: ICFF Film Summer Camp - Short Movie
DESCRIPTION:Short Movie Summer Camp - At The Distillery Historic District
 \, campers will engage in hands-on exploration of the filmmaking process 
 in both the morning and afternoon\, including pre-production\, production
  and post-production. In this camp\, participants will learn about cinema
 tography\, scriptwriting\, and editing. They will then create\, act in an
 d edit a short film and movie trailer. With access to our latest technolo
 gy\, including MacBooks\, 4K cameras\, tripods\, boom microphones and gre
 en screens\, participants will proudly present their short movie to paren
 ts\, showcasing all their hard work and creativity! This camp is in colla
 boration with Film Camp In a Box.
CATEGORIES:Film,Camp,Summer-Camp
