SUMMARY: Canadian Beer & Cheese Tour
DESCRIPTION:Book at https://www.gotourscanada.com/toronto-beer-cheese-tou
 r/\n\nDuration: Up to 2 hours\nBooking Times: Friday & Saturdays at 1:30 
 PM\n\n$95 Plus tax and 3% Booking Fee per person\n\nTaste local brews and
  Ontario Artisanal Cheeses\, while exploring the intricate history of Tor
 onto's Historic Distillery District. Your tour guide will share some of t
 heir favourite stories and sips along the way.\n\nBetween stops\, we shar
 e light and fascinating history of this popular area.\n\nMeet at our offi
 ce located at 11 Gristmill Lane.\n\n* Sorry no substitutions. Although we
  strive to be flexible we are limited by options from our food and drink 
 suppliers.
CATEGORIES:Beer,Cheese,Guided-Tour,Historical
